Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:04.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,およそ遠しとされしもの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:07.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,下等で奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:12.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,見慣れた動植物とはまるで違うと思しきもの達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:16.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それら異形の一群を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:19.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人は古くから畏れを含み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:22.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いつしか総じて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:24.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,「蟲」と呼んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ユリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:21.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ユリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ユリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,シゲル　あそこ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:47.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山に　取られたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:16.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イボ診てくれるってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲師だって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:20.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お医者じゃないのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こいつはいつ頃から？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この三日の内に皆が急にです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,足がしびれて辛いそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,皆困っております
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:42.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが山に入ったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だから死が伝染ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,死が伝染る？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,四日前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,亡くなった者がありましてな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この里では　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:06.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの山のあちこちにある沼地に死者を置いて葬るのです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,するとやがて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:14.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,骸は骨まで消えて　衣のみとなる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山へ帰るのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,我々は思っております
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:27.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ですが　それが終わるまで　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:31.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,七日間は山へ入ってはならんのです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:38.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,遠い昔　それを破った者が病を持ち帰り
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:42.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,里じゅうに広めたという言い伝えがあるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:48.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それゆえ皆　恐れておるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これは　「骸草」の芽か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:01.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,動物の骸を骨まで分解して　泥状にする蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:07.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その泥を生体に踏まれる事で　子株を広げ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:12.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それを　また踏んだ生体に寄生してゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,言い伝えとも重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:18.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,間違いないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これを　試してみてください
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:42.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,取れた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イボが取れたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,しびれも治った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あった　これだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,草全体には　塩を…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あのう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前さんも薬がいるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父さんを　診てあげて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,抜いても抜いても　生えてくるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,抜くと手にまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,薬が効かない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,他の者と明らかに違う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山に入ったのはあんたか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:07.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:12.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,死んだのは　俺の弟でな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この子と山へ供養に行ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何故掟を破ってまで？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:25.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんな言い伝えは嘘だと思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:31.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,十年前　俺の娘がいなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,捜すと山で衣だけが見つかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,皆　山に取られたのだと言った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:49.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　思えば　山に入った誰も病にはならなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だから　大丈夫だと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:58.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,弟さんの骸が　山に帰るところを見たのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:16.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さんに　会いたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:21.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山に　ひとりにするなんて　かわいそうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:23.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:29.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度　お別れを言いに行くか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだ　この草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:53.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,このっ　このっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さん　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:15.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当にもう山の一部になったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:24.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この草　父さんの分を　生きてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあ　もう戻ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ひとりになってしまったな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:51.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前　うちの子供になるか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:56.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おじさんを父さんの代わりと思ってくれ　な？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあ　帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう　泣くな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:09.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その日以来　足から草の芽が生えてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:12.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,日に日に育っている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:16.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,妙だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:22.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山で偶然　泥状の骸を踏み　病となった例は割りとある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:27.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　どれも薬で難なく治っている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何が違う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,骸と血縁があるという事か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:37.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　なら甥も条件は同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何か原因は他にある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:46.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,故意に骸のある場所へ行き　泥を踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:56.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,供養に行った者の足に泥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,弟さんはどんな亡くなり方を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:08.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,草介　お前は外へ行っておいで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:15.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,崖から落ちてな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:18.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,打ち所が悪かったか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,見つかった時にはもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あいつはいつも　俺を慕ってくれてた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,特別　仲のいい兄弟だったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辛かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父さん　治った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　まだわからん事があってな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前さんも　薬塗っとくか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:50.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おれはいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:54.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この草
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:57.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さんの代わりに生えてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも辛いだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:05.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,親父さんもお前さんを苦しめたくはないんじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:13.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　まだ無理なら　薬は伯父さんに預けとく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:15.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その気になったら　使うといい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:26.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,な　親父さんと伯父さんとはどんな兄弟だった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:34.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さんは伯父さんのこと　大好きだったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:39.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,小さい頃はよく伯父さんとの思い出話をしてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　何年か前から
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:46.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あまり伯父さんのこと話さなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,兄さん　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:17.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,兄さん　話したいことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ　シノブ　思い詰めた顔して　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何でも言えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,兄さん　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:59.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ユリは　俺が死なせてしまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ユリがいると知らずに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,荷車の下敷きに…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,兄さんに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:17.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,言えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:23.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そのまま山へ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すまない　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,兄さん　すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:42.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺も　子を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:49.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの子を見るたび苦しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:55.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしてこんなことを…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:49.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,兄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:55.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:00.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もういい　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もういい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前は死んだんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前　まだ生きてるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:42.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,草介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:53.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さんは昔ある人にひどいことをしてしまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:58.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もしも父さんに何かあっても
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前は誰も恨んだりしないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:12.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何　この里の者はいつかは皆山に帰るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:18.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何も心配することはない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:35.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一つ考えが浮かびましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　試しに聞いてみてください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:44.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その足に生えているのは　骸草という蟲だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:48.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,普段は泥状のものだが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:51.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,生き物の屍臭に反応し　死骸から芽を出す
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その芽を踏むと寄生されるが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,生きたものから芽を出しても育つことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:04.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　あんたのは骸と同じ反応をしている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:12.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたの体に屍臭が染みついているからと考えると筋が通る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一体　何のことを言っている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それを追及するつもりはない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この考えが正しければ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,僅かな屍臭も残さぬよう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,しっかりと洗い清めれば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,薬も効くようになるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,心当たりがあるなら　試してみるといい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:43.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺が口を出すのはここまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さんを殺したの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:24.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何を言ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:30.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,聞いてたんだ　さっきの蟲師さんの話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:38.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そのことを誰かに言ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ううん　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺　誰にも言わないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さんは誰も恨むなって言ったから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:59.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父さんは俺に優しくしてくれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:03.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なのにどうして　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなことしてしまったの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:13.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,怒りでどうしようもなくなってな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だがもし　あの時堪えられたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:24.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どの道いつかはこうなってただろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前だっていつかは俺を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,足が…草介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:48.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,早く　助け…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だこりゃ　踏んじまった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,下見て歩けよ
